Market Analysis and Insights

One of the primary factors driving the growth of the global video laryngoscope market is the growing prevalence of chronic obstructive pulmonary disease (COPD). The rising frequency of surgeries across diverse medical specialties also influence the market. However, insurance coverage and reimbursement issues are restraining the market growth.

